        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "No, I think we’ve covered everything. I’m all set. Thanks again for your help.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-02T07:43:38.122Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
          "text": "You’re very welcome, John. I’m glad everything’s covered. You’re all set with the plan, and I appreciate your time. Take care now.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-02T07:43:41.899Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "user",
          "text": "Will do. Take care, and thanks again.",
          "timestamp": "2026-02-02T07:43:46.122Z"
        },
        {
          "role": "agent",
